===============================
2007-11-09 - Major rewrite - Skip to 0.2.0
2007-10-16 - Concept with Level I clients removed.
2007-10-16 - Daemon UDP interface removed.
2007-10-05 - Shared memory interfaces removed both for Level I and Level II.
